# demo_outputs/

This directory is created at runtime by `run_demo.py`.

Files written here:
- `explain_output.txt`   — output from the Explain template
- `summarize_output.txt` — output from the Summarize template
- `questions_output.txt` — output from Generate Questions template
- `debug_output.txt`     — output from the Debug template
- `demo_report.pdf`      — full PDF brief of all 4 template outputs
- `demo_notes.md`        — Markdown notes of all 4 template outputs

Run `python run_demo.py` from the project root to generate these files.
